# 🌐 Portfolio Website

A simple personal portfolio website built using HTML and CSS.

## 📌 Features
- About Me section
- Skills section
- Projects section
- Education section
- Contact section

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS

## ▶️ How to View

1. Download the `index.html` file
2. Open it in any browser (Chrome, Firefox)
3. That's it! ✅

